hcc_text: Jerome Avenue is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top third for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Jerome Avenue at Major Deegan Exwy Sb En Jerome A, Major Deegan Exwy Nb Exit 13, Major Deegan Exwy Sb Exit 13 and East 233rd Street, there were 3 severe injuries in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
